{"tid":1696351,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"今日Now有人Phone In話催淚煙殘留洗完會出綠色水, 我懷疑係d係有氯氣成份","createTime":"2019-11-06T06:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T11:56:52.000Z","uid":12599,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f13387aff0911617cf019b68b82908c59630af63","tid":1696351,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"今朝Now有多過一位聽眾phone in話洗完d空氣清新機出左d綠色水, 前幾日有d催淚彈掂到水之後出左d好vivid既藍色, 而家同大家研究下究竟係乜野東西來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DepKbVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDepKbVE.jpg&h=7a739a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n眾所周知山埃係係可以用來做電鍍或者製作染料, 當中最出名係一隻叫隻普魯士藍(Prussian Blue)既東西。呢樣野係鐵同山埃混合後既化學物(Ferrocyanide), 係人類藝術史上用過來製作唔少出名既畫作, 包括梵高既星夜同浮世繪名作神奈川沖浪裏, 對於呢隻化學物已經有人進一步研究, 而家研究下綠色水係咩東西, 詳細可以睇化學補習天王K Kwong分析: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/11383432157/photos/a.10155751654262158/10157555968972158/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F11383432157%2Fphotos%2Fa.10155751654262158%2F10157555968972158%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=f2bbf3e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/11383432157/photos/a.10155751654262158/10157555968972158/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n係2016年一篇對催淚煙的paper中(<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/&hellip;/medicine-and-denti&hellip;/tear-gas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fmedicine-and-denti%E2%80%A6%2Ftear-gas&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=e2e62903\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/&hellip;/medicine-and-denti&hellip;/tear-gas</a>), 講煙霧彈會加入諸如Hexachloroethane 同 Zinc Oxide以燃燒合成Zinc Chloride呢類比CS氣低一d刺激性既氣體<br />\n<br />\n不過呢...Zinc Chloride加水後係無色, 另一樣個人認為更有可能既化學物係催淚彈殼用nickel製作, 係高溫下同氯氣合成左Nickel Chloride, 唔同既化學組合下會出黃, 藍同綠色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.sciencephoto.com/image/c0279634/800wm/C0279634-Nickel_and_Zinc_Chloride.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.sciencephoto.com%2Fimage%2Fc0279634%2F800wm%2FC0279634-Nickel_and_Zinc_Chloride.jpg&h=d45f5b98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊係Nickel Chloride, 右邊係Zinc Chloride (<a href=\"https://www.sciencephoto.com/media/705806/view/nickel-and-zinc-chloride\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencephoto.com%2Fmedia%2F705806%2Fview%2Fnickel-and-zinc-chloride&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=4a2c54d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencephoto.com/media/705806/view/nickel-and-zinc-chloride</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oYXzzan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoYXzzan.jpg&h=4800a624&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n係呢個介紹Nickel Chloride特性既網站中(<a href=\"https://www.chemistryscl.com/advancedlevel/inorganic/qualitative_analysis/testing-for-nickel-ion/main.html?fbclid=IwAR3FIkr5e0mPe3tHunbt0v-c0RHtrZJmDQohOnNEBU77pK00Q5t33Yvga0o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chemistryscl.com%2Fadvancedlevel%2Finorganic%2Fqualitative_analysis%2Ftesting-for-nickel-ion%2Fmain.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3FIkr5e0mPe3tHunbt0v-c0RHtrZJmDQohOnNEBU77pK00Q5t33Yvga0o&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=85e094bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chemistryscl.com/advancedlevel/inorganic/qualitative_analysis/testing-for-nickel-ion/main.html?fbclid=IwAR3FIkr5e0mPe3tHunbt0v-c0RHtrZJmDQohOnNEBU77pK00Q5t33Yvga0o</a>), 如果aqeous form下有ethanol medium 先會出藍色, 如果催淚彈有hexachloroethane同nickel合金彈殼有化學作用, 以上推論係成立既<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為轉左做氯氣唔係山埃氣就覺得無乜野, 氯氣正正係人類歷史上第一隻投入戰場既化武, 係一戰後因為殺傷力太大已經完全禁止係任何戰爭中使用。(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemical_weapons_in_World_War_I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FChemical_weapons_in_World_War_I&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=e0c787ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemical_weapons_in_World_War_I</a>)<br />\n<br />\n氯氣係通過與呼吸道水份合成HCl, 即係鹽酸, 三大強酸之一, 胃酸主要成份。進入氣管入肺會燒傷d軟組織導致呼吸困難<br />\n<br />\n我既chem知識只係10幾年前考CE既程度, 以上全屬個人推測。如果下次有人洗冷氣出左D綠色催淚水出來, 可以拎d sample俾大學實驗室做下mass spec驗證下我既推論。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. d前線清潔工係無資方(即係政府外判商)俾既保護裝備, 最多都係自費買對手套同手術口罩, 呢班清潔工人工低之餘仲要硬食催淚彈殘餘, 係無充足保護裝備下工作係可以考慮下告勞工條例"},{"pid":"9d761df3fd69c961018d59dae373a1ab162b63bc","tid":1696351,"uid":48605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"仆街曱甴 亂尻咁放"},{"pid":"6e934bc952acdccff3542b866036e3fcd6c76f56","tid":1696351,"uid":74272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:28:47.000Z","msg":"D清潔工好慘"},{"pid":"4409cd84c4c6f5bcd2c3a389be4a4b60fffa59ea","tid":1696351,"uid":208391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:29:02.000Z","msg":"Puhs"},{"pid":"50567330cdeb964115ff34ecad9090cc87301b02","tid":1696351,"uid":208391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:29:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7551f0910d000841021c7297616830af4ae5d589","tid":1696351,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66542881b27f35097da3e8a0a3ab082dd0d99c4","tid":1696351,"uid":225977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:30:51.000Z","msg":"殺人政權毒殺市民"},{"pid":"dae77a77a7b371893709a11bae3806689141c602","tid":1696351,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e5a46f9a03fa8a65d1ac215b5fbb2e1b55dc5b","tid":1696351,"uid":328969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:35:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea7c4a4b957a75c04ff15d2f9dcb9b26ae791bc6","tid":1696351,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:38:14.000Z","msg":"Low Quality Tear Gas = Poison Weapon"},{"pid":"2431a3a24c7a201ef1fc1421bec5f244fc27e249","tid":1696351,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ba6b657b210770ed8114eab32fc8d90fed28e4","tid":1696351,"uid":159413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:42:28.000Z","msg":"隔離post 有講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n化學博士: 點解最近D催淚彈咁多煙同咁高温？長文慢慢睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1695932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1695932</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6be6ea992aea26e150c37bfc8b7554628f1b8029","tid":1696351,"uid":63298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:42:51.000Z","msg":"之前有team人發表過化驗報告?<br />\n聯絡佢地俾啲資料佢地先?"},{"pid":"0accf99415bfb86a07e5817b5c471c9eac45ec04","tid":1696351,"uid":51057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:43:29.000Z","msg":"習近平 曱甴王 甴近平"},{"pid":"b746f7597aedc6f011b968e731e37111032bd8fb","tid":1696351,"uid":115279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1985482dd588f8233552f8f643a4e9af2173b6da","tid":1696351,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"補返岩zinc chloride 既link: <a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/tear-gas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Ftopics%2Fmedicine-and-dentistry%2Ftear-gas&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=4289fb59\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/medicine-and-dentistry/tear-gas</a>"},{"pid":"ea802f0b9fab3b0d4821ae6f4c71dbe7174dcea8","tid":1696351,"uid":106027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a36ba71ea14ccf7d970aed0b108dcd55fd3d5db","tid":1696351,"uid":28628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f13387aff0911617cf019b68b82908c59630af63","tid":1696351,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"今朝Now有多過一位聽眾phone in話洗完d空氣清新機出左d綠色水, 前幾日有d催淚彈掂到水之後出左d好vivid既藍色, 而家同大家研究下究竟係乜野東西來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DepKbVE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDepKbVE.jpg&h=7a739a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n眾所周知山埃係係可以用來做電鍍或者製作染料, 當中最出名係一隻叫隻普魯士藍(Prussian Blue)既東西。呢樣野係鐵同山埃混合後既化學物(Ferrocyanide), 係人類藝術史上用過來製作唔少出名既畫作, 包括梵高既星夜同浮世繪名作神奈川沖浪裏, 對於呢隻化學物已經有人進一步研究, 而家研究下綠色水係咩東西, 詳細可以睇化學補習天王K Kwong分析: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/11383432157/photos/a.10155751654262158/10157555968972158/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F11383432157%2Fphotos%2Fa.10155751654262158%2F10157555968972158%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=f2bbf3e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/11383432157/photos/a.10155751654262158/10157555968972158/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n係2016年一篇對催淚煙的paper中(<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/&hellip;/medicine-and-denti&hellip;/tear-gas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2Fmedicine-and-denti%E2%80%A6%2Ftear-gas&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=e2e62903\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/&hellip;/medicine-and-denti&hellip;/tear-gas</a>), 講煙霧彈會加入諸如Hexachloroethane 同 Zinc Oxide以燃燒合成Zinc Chloride呢類比CS氣低一d刺激性既氣體<br />\n<br />\n不過呢...Zinc Chloride加水後係無色, 另一樣個人認為更有可能既化學物係催淚彈殼用nickel製作, 係高溫下同氯氣合成左Nickel Chloride, 唔同既化學組合下會出黃, 藍同綠色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.sciencephoto.com/image/c0279634/800wm/C0279634-Nickel_and_Zinc_Chloride.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.sciencephoto.com%2Fimage%2Fc0279634%2F800wm%2FC0279634-Nickel_and_Zinc_Chloride.jpg&h=d45f5b98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊係Nickel Chloride, 右邊係Zinc Chloride (<a href=\"https://www.sciencephoto.com/media/705806/view/nickel-and-zinc-chloride\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencephoto.com%2Fmedia%2F705806%2Fview%2Fnickel-and-zinc-chloride&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=4a2c54d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencephoto.com/media/705806/view/nickel-and-zinc-chloride</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oYXzzan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoYXzzan.jpg&h=4800a624&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n係呢個介紹Nickel Chloride特性既網站中(<a href=\"https://www.chemistryscl.com/advancedlevel/inorganic/qualitative_analysis/testing-for-nickel-ion/main.html?fbclid=IwAR3FIkr5e0mPe3tHunbt0v-c0RHtrZJmDQohOnNEBU77pK00Q5t33Yvga0o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chemistryscl.com%2Fadvancedlevel%2Finorganic%2Fqualitative_analysis%2Ftesting-for-nickel-ion%2Fmain.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3FIkr5e0mPe3tHunbt0v-c0RHtrZJmDQohOnNEBU77pK00Q5t33Yvga0o&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=85e094bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chemistryscl.com/advancedlevel/inorganic/qualitative_analysis/testing-for-nickel-ion/main.html?fbclid=IwAR3FIkr5e0mPe3tHunbt0v-c0RHtrZJmDQohOnNEBU77pK00Q5t33Yvga0o</a>), 如果aqeous form下有ethanol medium 先會出藍色, 如果催淚彈有hexachloroethane同nickel合金彈殼有化學作用, 以上推論係成立既<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為轉左做氯氣唔係山埃氣就覺得無乜野, 氯氣正正係人類歷史上第一隻投入戰場既化武, 係一戰後因為殺傷力太大已經完全禁止係任何戰爭中使用。(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemical_weapons_in_World_War_I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FChemical_weapons_in_World_War_I&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnX1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=e0c787ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemical_weapons_in_World_War_I</a>)<br />\n<br />\n氯氣係通過與呼吸道水份合成HCl, 即係鹽酸, 三大強酸之一, 胃酸主要成份。進入氣管入肺會燒傷d軟組織導致呼吸困難<br />\n<br />\n我既chem知識只係10幾年前考CE既程度, 以上全屬個人推測。如果下次有人洗冷氣出左D綠色催淚水出來, 可以拎d sample俾大學實驗室做下mass spec驗證下我既推論。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. d前線清潔工係無資方(即係政府外判商)俾既保護裝備, 最多都係自費買對手套同手術口罩, 呢班清潔工人工低之餘仲要硬食催淚彈殘餘, 係無充足保護裝備下工作係可以考慮下告勞工條例"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:54:17.000Z","msg":"Chlorine 同chloride 兩回事嚟<br />\nAqueous fe2+ ions 都係咁上下顏色<br />\n<br />\nScience 唔係咁架<br />\n你呀爸有so <br />\n唔等如有so就係你呀爸<br />\n<br />\n交返比d真係識既人解釋啦<br />\n唔係到時d人又信以為係真<br />\n太多false message <br />\n<br />\n利申：chem PhD 緊"},{"pid":"cc82b399627f865e9dc4e94786e3a46504b00bef","tid":1696351,"uid":158555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:57:06.000Z","msg":"我啲尿偏綠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似菜蜜咁<br />\n有冇人一樣?"},{"pid":"d76efcb142cb8a257519ce346a1ce9dc45eb300a","tid":1696351,"uid":235477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"有無英文文宣講呢樣"},{"pid":"a62c099f21acb50e0b63e39ee3de175705c4677e","tid":1696351,"uid":129054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:59:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac586b2c02db17c33d2fc97eb25912bf600643ff","tid":1696351,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a36ba71ea14ccf7d970aed0b108dcd55fd3d5db","tid":1696351,"uid":28628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f13387aff0911617cf019b68b82908c59630af63","tid":1696351,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"